message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and expectations. Given its exceptional value and quality, it is worth $15000 to you. Considering this, I am offering you the opportunity to acquire this product at an exclusive price of $12000. This offer reflects a strategic compromise that aims to ensure both parties benefit from this transaction. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to serve you with excellence.
